GetAngles (script event)
========================

Game class
----------

This event operates on an instance of the [Game\_class.html game class] type {{{gameclass}}}

Description
-----------

Returns the current orientation of this entity (relative to bind parent if any).

Usage
-----

*vector* getAngles()

Parameters
----------

This script event does not accept parameters.

Examples
--------

` `
`angles = `<font color="#000055">`$player1`</font>`.`<font color="#ff0000">`getAngles`</font><font color="#000000">`(`</font><font color="#000000">`)`</font>`;`

Notes
-----

This script event returns the orientation of this entity as a vector.


